Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the blunder I've committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not responsible for anything, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has been seized, and we are currently searching for the crew throughout the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will find them in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.00,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found them?! Keep searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like quite the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has there been a break-in or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't hurt me! If you must, do it gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. Scarron-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You weren't followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that you were all being held in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To give up the status of an aristocrat just to help a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so idiotic that I could expect it only from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get out, but what's our plan from here on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The city's crawling with guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll walk to Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, take a look at this map.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll first fly the Ostland to Germania, in the opposite direction of Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The military will think we're going to enter Gallia via Germania, so they'll come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when we take the chance to walk into Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Head over to the former territory of Orléans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is where Miss Tabitha's residence is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might find some clues there, is that the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys thinking of going all the way to Gallian Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disobey the Queen that much, that will be a serious felony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only will they take your titles away,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you might experience something even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Since Tabitha's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my dear sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can never find a cure for idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica, give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sensei, to use the Ostland as a distraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to go back to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. By the timing of the escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's obvious the Ostland assisted in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure guards have been stationed on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the Ostland to me. You should all make haste to Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean! Are you serious about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't put you in such danger alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one in greatest danger now is Miss Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to lose by arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can help with manoeuvring the Ostland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll be of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go anywhere with you, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I am your personal maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Saito is no longer a chevalier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he doesn't need a personal maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a chevalier has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer an aristocrat either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't want to hear a plebeian boss me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, both of you. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the time to argue over thing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.40,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, what are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You make the choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed how they can keep going with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did Jessica and Scarron go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some time ago, a really poor travelling\Ncarnival left these for the food they ate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll catch you in no time with the clothes you're wearing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disguise yourselves in these and go to Gallia or wherever you need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But promise to save your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I won't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can now save Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.99,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.09,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Très bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So nice. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing all of this for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Tabitha is my student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even saved me by making me appear dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an obligation to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean! You really are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Miss Zerbst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys on the first floor and girls on the second floor. Get a move on and get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why are you laughing at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look perfect in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Those clothes! Those boots! That nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone looks absolutely lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot imagine exposing my belly in front of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad once in a while. You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there's a poor one who can't even get a gram of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it sound like I was talking about someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you really carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to save your best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what's with your messed up clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the mission will succeed if I furrow my\Nbrow and have a complicated look on like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does, then I would, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't work together, even things that are supposed to work won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up on going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any strength like you all do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll probably only be in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be on the Ostland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I can't take a frail girl like you on a dangerous journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to give up on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my heart will be with you no matter where you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for not being frail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a cocky dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been saying... Why are we fighting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we shall head to the Ostland to recover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun's party will go rescue Miss Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl captured by the dragon withheld her tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because she was the daughter of the people who\Nmistreated l'Ivaldi, and she thought she had no right to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This is a punishment for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment for betraying my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myoz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Myoz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been expecting you, Joseph-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the requested item would be ready soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I came rushing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On another note, this place is really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To not allow any air or sound to escape, this place is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we also have multiple furnaces and smelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. I'm more interested in the item.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Jormungand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's chained down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we expected, there are guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Colbert-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Str... Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They figured we'd head for the border, so they've set a checkpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find out who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I bet they'll throw us into the jail and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're disguised right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't see through us that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act normally as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you guys. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A travelling circus, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey fatty! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fatty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really worried there for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, scaring us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left now is to go over the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more until we get to Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Colbert-sensei will get the Ostland back without problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the troubled look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer an aristocrat either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't want to hear a plebeian boss me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. I'm no longer a Vallière, so I'm a plebeian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not related to Father, Mother, or my sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have Saito from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is off limits. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually have something even better to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dana tel winde!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oltal sleip cloudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, get aboard the Ostland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta-kun, you come to the bridge with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimli-kun and Reinard-kun, you two head to the engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw more coal in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! The soldiers are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Colbert! If we don't hurry, the pursuit force will come right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to lure them away until\NSaito-kun's party crosses the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you standing around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to cross the border into Germania and to Gallia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intercept them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go after them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looked pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I will dismiss all your past failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you've made quite the achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too great an honour for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is one thing that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? You don't look happy enough for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're being chased as traitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That void mage is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I presume their intent is to rescue Charlotte-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll face them before they enter Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitartial is at Al Hambra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before my niece falls into her eternal sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would like to see her friends once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu kept thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only the fact that she betrayed her friend remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So it's only natural for me to go through this."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu's last wish was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be forgiven by the friend she betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a wish that was not to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Since... there's no way..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...he'd forgive me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a large number after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, they'll catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's come down to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should attack them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see anyone get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have to climb much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining. Everyone's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to live alone from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only sprained my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rely on me at times like this, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might think of me as unreliable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that my ankle hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to reward my familiar once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm just letting you do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito's been alone in this world all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he still be so courageous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does he not get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I filled with so much anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! The Dragon Knights are right behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more than this will be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the four of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should have crossed the border by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Agnes-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I was fooled by you thrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! If I don't take you guys back, I cannot face the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Gallian Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha... We're coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission only someone as cute as I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captive in Al Hambra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
